// -------------------------
      // Shared cross-pack coordination.
      // Multiple aircraft-family sound packs may be loaded at once.
      // Native GeoFS audio should be muted if ANY pack currently claims
      // the loaded aircraft, and restored only when NONE do. Each pack
      // writes its own boolean into a shared registry; a single arbiter
      // (installed once, by whichever pack's code runs first) reads the
